    "title": "Scientists thread rows of metal atoms into nanofiber bundles",
    "body": "2023/04/03 - Our collaborative paper in van der Waals nanofibers of atomically thin W6Te6 wires was selected by Tokyo Metropolitan University news, EurekAlert!, etc. with the title ‚ÄúScientists thread rows of metal atoms into nanofiber bundles‚Äù. More information: R. Natsui et al. Vapor-Phase Indium Intercalation in van der Waals Nanofibers of Atomically Thin W6Te6 Wires, ACS Nano 17, 5561‚Äì5569 (2023). "
